      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:1.05rem;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.8;">Your site, fully managed by you — no developer needed after launch. I build a private admin dashboard so you can update content, manage orders, view inquiries, and run your business from any device.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:20px;text-align:left;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:10px;">&#9776;</div>
          <h4 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;font-size:0.95rem;">Content Management</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6;">Edit pages, blog posts, and images directly from a clean admin panel. No code required.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:10px;">&#9993;</div>
          <h4 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;font-size:0.95rem;">Leads &amp; Inquiries</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6;">Every form submission, quote request, and contact lands in your dashboard — organized and searchable.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:10px;">&#9632;</div>
          <h4 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;font-size:0.95rem;">Store &amp; Products</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6;">Sell digital products, services, or subscriptions with built-in Stripe payments and order tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:10px;">&#9679;</div>
          <h4 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;font-size:0.95rem;">Data &amp; Analytics</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6;">Revenue totals, visitor trends, and business metrics — all in a clean dashboard built for your specific needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.88rem;margin-bottom:24px;">Powered by Node.js, SQLite, and a fully custom admin panel — the same stack behind Enduring Branches. Built for your business, owned by you.</p>
      <a href="/quote" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:1rem;padding:14px 36px;">Request a CMS Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SETUP PROCESS -->
<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How the Done-For-You Setup Works</h2>
      <p>From deposit to live site in less than a week.</p>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-steps" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step-num">1</div>
        <h3>Pick a Template</h3>
        <p>Browse the templates and choose the one that fits your business. Or tell me your industry and I'll recommend one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step-num">2</div>
        <h3>Pay $200 Deposit</h3>
        <p>Secure checkout via Stripe. I'll reach out within 24 hours to collect your content — logo, photos, text.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step-num">3</div>
        <h3>I Build It</h3>
        <p>I customize the template with your branding and content. You get a preview link to approve before it goes live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step-num">4</div>
        <h3>You Launch</h3>
        <p>Once you approve, I connect your domain and flip the switch. Your site is live — you own every file.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SETUP FORM -->
<section class="section" id="setup-form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="form-card">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:6px;">Start Your Done-For-You Setup</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:28px;">Fill out the form below and you'll be taken to a secure $200 deposit checkout. I'll be in touch within 24 hours.</p>
      <form action="/setup/none" method="POST">
        <div class="form-2col">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Jane Smith" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="jane@example.com" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-2col">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) 000-0000" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="business_name">Business Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="business_name" name="business_name" placeholder="Smith Pressure Washing" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="business_url">Current Website (if any)</label>
          <input type="url" id="business_url" name="business_url" placeholder="https://..." />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="notes">Anything else I should know?</label>
          <textarea id="notes" name="notes" rows="4" placeholder="Which template are you interested in? Any specific colors or style notes?"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold btn-full" style="font-size:1rem;padding:14px;">Pay $200 Deposit &amp; Get Started &rarr;</button>
        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--gray);text-align:center;margin-top:10px;">Secure checkout via Stripe. Deposit is applied toward the total project cost.</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
